objects.description: [Aquatic Panda](https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0143) has used DLL search-order hijacking to load `exe`, `dll`, and `dat` files into memory.(Citation: CrowdStrike AQUATIC PANDA December 2021) [Aquatic Panda](https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0143) loaded a malicious DLL into the legitimate Windows Security Health Service executable (SecurityHealthService.exe) to execute malicious code on victim systems.(Citation: Crowdstrike HuntReport 2022)
